presidents  partners at institutional investment firms and  ernst  young entrepreneur of the year award winnersunder the terms of the agreement desco will continue to provide industry leading products service and support that customers have come to expect and all license and service agreements will be maintained the highland creek team will bring decades of experience successfully growing technology businesses and will serve as advisors and directors for desco going forward dean e schreiner will step down as owner and ceo but will remain involved with the business as a senior advisor“i strongly believe that this partnership best positions the company to execute on our vision of providing the most innovative software solutions to the service industry” said dean e schreiner “desco will gain financial flexibility and strong managerial expertise to better serve our customers and execute on our longterm strategy we are excited to work with our new partners at highland creek and enter our next chapter of growth and industry leadership”for the transaction highland creek was advised by mcdonald hopkins llc and hood and strong llp lending for the deal was provided by avidbankfor any questions please contact karacrider director marketing karacdescosoftcomabout desco llcdesco llc is the leading developer of innovative service management software for the service industry headquartered in fort myers florida desco serves more than 3 service verticals both nationally and internationally descos flagship product electronic service control esc is a comprehensive service management solution that enables companies to easily manage customers work and finances esc provides the tools and features growing and profitable service companies need for success for more information visit wwwdescosoftcom or contact us at 8679about highland creek partnershighland creek partners is backed by over  seasoned entrepreneurs executives and investors a group that includes  current and former ceopresidents